{% comment %}
  Brand Page: Incubator — The Experimental Arm
  PERSONA: Futuristic, conceptual, lab-born. Divergent thinking meets streetwear.
  Neon green (#00FF88) on dark (#050505). Grid-tech aesthetic. Outside The Box.
{% endcomment %}

{%- assign incu_col = collections['incubator'] -%}

<!-- ============================================================
     HERO — Dark lab aesthetic with scanning grid + neon pulse
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="ib-hero" id="ib-top">
  <!-- Animated scan lines -->
  <div class="ib-scan" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <!-- Grid overlay -->
  <div class="ib-grid-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <!-- Neon glow orbs -->
  <div class="ib-orb ib-orb1" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="ib-orb ib-orb2" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- Floating code fragments -->
  <div class="ib-code-frags" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="ib-frag ib-f1">{ divergent: true }</span>
    <span class="ib-frag ib-f2">// outside the box</span>
    <span class="ib-frag ib-f3">init()</span>
    <span class="ib-frag ib-f4">→ experiment</span>
    <span class="ib-frag ib-f5">[ prototype ]</span>
  </div>

  <div class="ib-hero-inner">
    <div class="ib-hero-meta">
      <span class="ib-meta-badge">08</span>
      <span class="ib-meta-line"></span>
      <span class="ib-meta-text">Sub-Brand / Experimental Arm</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="ib-hero-title">INCUBA<em>TOR</em></h1>

    <p class="ib-hero-tagline">What is the <span class="ib-neon">Incubator?</span></p>

    <p class="ib-hero-desc">The Incubator is an invention of multi-media artist and art director, Anthony Cooper, founder of the Have A Nice Day brands. Having collaborated with many artists over the years, he wanted to help create graphic superstars, rather than the brands stealing all the limelight — after realising that streetwear brands change hands for a small fortune, with often no nod or reward to the artists who helped create them.</p>

    <div class="ib-hero-cta-row">
      <a class="ib-cta-main" href="#ib-shop">
        Enter The Lab
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14m-7-7l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
      <div class="ib-hero-stats">
        <div class="ib-hs"><span class="ib-hs-n">∞</span><span class="ib-hs-l">Concepts</span></div>
        <div class="ib-hs-div"></div>
        <div class="ib-hs"><span class="ib-hs-n">LTD</span><span class="ib-hs-l">Editions</span></div>
        <div class="ib-hs-div"></div>
        <div class="ib-hs"><span class="ib-hs-n">UK</span><span class="ib-hs-l">Lab-Made</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ib-scroll-cue">
    <div class="ib-scroll-bar"></div>
    <span>Scroll</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     MARQUEE — Glitch ticker
     ============================================================ -->
<div class="ib-marquee">
  <div class="ib-mq-track">
    {%- for i in (1..3) -%}
    <span class="ib-mq-w">INCUBATOR</span><span class="ib-mq-dot">◆</span>
    <span class="ib-mq-w ib-mq-outline">DIVERGENT</span><span class="ib-mq-dot">◆</span>
    <span class="ib-mq-w">OUTSIDE THE BOX</span><span class="ib-mq-dot">◆</span>
    <span class="ib-mq-w ib-mq-outline">PROTOTYPE</span><span class="ib-mq-dot">◆</span>
    <span class="ib-mq-w">CAMDEN LAB</span><span class="ib-mq-dot">◆</span>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============================================================
     STORY — Lab concept editorial
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="ib-story">
  <div class="ib-story-grid">
    <div class="ib-story-lhs">
      <div class="ib-lab-badge">
        <svg class="ib-dna" viewBox="0 0 100 100" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,255,136,.15)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="30" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,255,136,.1)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="15" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,255,136,.08)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="4" fill="#00FF88"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="ib-lab-text">LAB<br>008</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ib-concept-tags">
        <span>Prototype</span><span>Divergent</span><span>Outside The Box</span><span>Experimental</span><span>Camden Lab</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ib-story-rhs">
      <div class="ib-eyebrow"><span class="ib-eye-pulse"></span>The Submission Process</div>
      <h2 class="ib-story-h2">
        <span>Submit your</span>
        <span class="ib-h2-neon">designs.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="ib-story-p">Artists or new brands are offered the monthly opportunity to digitally submit a biog and links to your social media and between 4 to 8 designs, which will be available across 4 garments — T-shirts, Long Sleeve Tees, Sweats and Hoodies — in 4 colours of your choice!</p>
      <p class="ib-story-p">The <em>only</em> condition of a submission is having 50 followers! The month's winner designs will be uploaded the following month and given <strong>100 days</strong> to sell <strong>100 garments</strong>. This submission process will be available by country or territory, making the process local to each market.</p>
      <p class="ib-story-p">The first 10 brand submissions will have the opportunity to have a 30 min WhatsApp video call with an art director, should they want to discuss their product. Submissions will be closed for the month after the first 10 brands have been submitted — so what are you waiting for?</p>
      <div class="ib-specs">
        <div class="ib-spec"><span class="ib-spec-k">Challenge</span><span class="ib-spec-v">100 Sales in 100 Days</span></div>
        <div class="ib-spec"><span class="ib-spec-k">Royalty</span><span class="ib-spec-v">5% of Net Sale</span></div>
        <div class="ib-spec"><span class="ib-spec-k">Garments</span><span class="ib-spec-v">Tees · Longsleeves · Sweats · Hoodies</span></div>
        <div class="ib-spec"><span class="ib-spec-k">Submit To</span><span class="ib-spec-v ib-neon">robert@dreadyoriginal.com</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     BENEFITS & REWARDS
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="ib-benefits">
  <div class="ib-benefits-inner">
    <div class="ib-eyebrow"><span class="ib-eye-pulse"></span>Benefits &amp; Rewards</div>
    <h2 class="ib-benefits-h2">Incubator <span class="ib-neon">rewards.</span></h2>

    <div class="ib-benefits-grid">
      <div class="ib-benefit-card">
        <div class="ib-benefit-icon">🏷️</div>
        <h3>Printed Neck Label</h3>
        <p>Each new brand will come with a printed Incubator neck label, making it a potentially collectible — and of course a Limited Edition / Investment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ib-benefit-card">
        <h3>5% Royalty</h3>
        <div class="ib-benefit-icon">💰</div>
        <p>For each shirt sold, you will receive a 5% royalty of the net sale, i.e. after VAT or the equivalent local tax.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ib-benefit-card">
        <div class="ib-benefit-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3>100 Days / 100 Sales</h3>
        <p>If after 100 days, 100 shirts have been sold you will have the option of remaining on the site, on a non-exclusive basis, as a fully fledged brand, with the full range of garments, stickers etc — now upgraded to our standard 10% of the net royalty.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ib-benefit-card">
        <div class="ib-benefit-icon">🤝</div>
        <h3>Partnerships</h3>
        <p>If it is a partnership, the artist will get 2% and the partners the 8% balance — if they so choose. This enables the artist royalty to be split between artists, enabling collaborations on new brands and ideas!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ib-sticker-option">
      <div class="ib-sticker-badge">STICKER OPTION</div>
      <p>If you would like to invest in 30 A5 custom sticker sheets @ £60 + P&amp;P (which works out at £2 a sheet, Recommended Retail Price £5), we will <strong>not only</strong> offer them for sale on the site as part of your offering, but also supply a free sheet at our own expense, with each and every purchase made — thereby helping spread the word!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     ARTIST BIOG — Incubator No. 1: DIVERGENT
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="ib-artist">
  <div class="ib-artist-inner">
    <div class="ib-eyebrow"><span class="ib-eye-pulse"></span>Incubator No.1</div>
    <h2 class="ib-artist-h2">DIVERGENT</h2>
    <div class="ib-artist-subtitle">Introducing <span class="ib-neon">Phillip Long</span></div>

    <!-- Divergent Original Instagram -->
    <a class="ib-divergent-ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/divergentoriginal/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
      <span>@divergentoriginal</span>
    </a>

    <div class="ib-artist-biog">
      <p>About Phillip Long — Founder of Nagual Creations. Phillip Long is a British artist whose career began in the early 1990s at the heart of London's underground rave scene. Through his visionary project, Nagual Creations, he pioneered large-scale, immersive artworks that brought a new level of depth and atmosphere to music and multimedia events across the world — from iconic London clubs to mountaintops in Japan and deserts in South Africa.</p>
      <p>Though the setting has shifted from dance floors to living rooms and galleries, Phillip's work still offers an invitation into an otherworldly, immersive experience — one where imagination and emotion meet in rich visual form. Phillip also spent 5 years as an art director for a London marketing agency, where he honed his skills in graphic design, which he now teaches part time at Far Skate Foundation in Whitstable.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ib-artist-submit">
      <p><strong>Want to submit your designs?</strong> Send your biog, social media links and 4–8 designs to: <a href="mailto:robert@dreadyoriginal.com" class="ib-neon">robert@dreadyoriginal.com</a></p>
      <p>Finally, if you are a fan of the Incubator concept and logo, please feel free to purchase an Incubator branded shirt!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     PRODUCTS
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="ib-shop hand-sec" id="ib-shop">
  <div class="hand-container">

    <div class="hand-grid ib-grid" id="ib-product-grid">
      {%- if incu_col and incu_col.products.size > 0 -%}
        {%- for product in incu_col.products -%}
          <a class="hand-card ib-card" href="{{ product.url }}">
            <div class="imgwrap">
              <span class="tag">{{ product.type | default: 'Lab' }}</span>
              {%- if product.featured_image -%}
                <img src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }}" alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | default: product.title }}" loading="lazy" />
              {%- else -%}
                <div style="width:100%;height:340px;background:#0a0a0a;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
                  <span style="color:#00FF88;font-family:monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;">PROTOTYPE</span>
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
              <span class="quick">View Experiment →</span>
            </div>
            <div class="body">
              <div class="name">{{ product.title }}</div>
              <div class="row2">
                <div class="price">{{ product.price | money }}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        {%- endfor -%}
      {%- else -%}
        <!-- Fallback: pull from all products tagged 'incubator' or show message -->
        <div class="ib-empty">
          <div class="ib-empty-icon">⟐</div>
          <h3>Experiments In Progress</h3>
          <p>The next Incubator drop is being prototyped in the Camden lab. Sign up to be first to know.</p>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
    <!-- View All Products CTA -->
    <div style="text-align:center;padding:3rem 0 1.5rem">
      <a href="/collections/incubator" style="display:inline-block;font-family:var(--mono,'JetBrains Mono',monospace);font-size:.95rem;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fff;background:transparent;border:2px solid #fff;padding:1.1rem 3.5rem;text-decoration:none;transition:all .3s ease" onmouseover="this.style.background='#fff';this.style.color='#0a0a0a'" onmouseout="this.style.background='transparent';this.style.color='#fff'">VIEW ALL INCUBATOR PRODUCTS →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     CTA — Join the experiment
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="ib-cta">
  <div class="ib-cta-inner">
    <div class="ib-cta-badge">↗</div>
    <h2 class="ib-cta-h2">Think <span class="ib-neon">different.</span><br>Wear different.</h2>
    <p>The Incubator is always looking for collaborators, artists, and divergent thinkers. If you've got an idea that doesn't fit anywhere else — it fits here.</p>
    <div class="ib-cta-btns">
      <a class="ib-cta-main" href="/pages/contact">Get In Touch →</a>
      <a class="ib-cta-ghost" href="/collections/all">Browse All Brands</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     STYLES
     ============================================================ -->
<style>
:root {
  --ib-bg: #050505;
  --ib-fg: #e8e8e8;
  --ib-neon: #00FF88;
  --ib-neon2: #00D4FF;
  --ib-dim: #333;
  --ib-surface: #0c0c0c;
}

/* === HERO === */
.ib-hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: var(--ib-bg);
  color: var(--ib-fg);
  overflow: hidden;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 120px 0 80px;
}
.ib-grid-bg {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,255,136,.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,255,136,.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.ib-scan {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(
    0deg,
    transparent, transparent 2px,
    rgba(0,255,136,.02) 2px, rgba(0,255,136,.02) 4px
  );
  pointer-events: none;
  animation: ib-scan-move 8s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes ib-scan-move {
  0% { transform: translateY(0); }
  100% { transform: translateY(60px); }
}
.ib-orb {
  position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(80px); pointer-events: none;
}
.ib-orb1 {
  width: 500px; height: 500px; top: -10%; right: -5%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,255,136,.15), transparent 70%);
}
.ib-orb2 {
  width: 400px; height: 400px; bottom: 5%; left: -5%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,212,255,.1), transparent 70%);
}
.ib-code-frags {
  position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
}
.ib-frag {
  position: absolute;
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .15em;
  color: rgba(0,255,136,.12); text-transform: uppercase;
}
.ib-f1 { top: 15%; right: 8%; }
.ib-f2 { top: 35%; right: 15%; }
.ib-f3 { bottom: 25%; left: 5%; }
.ib-f4 { top: 60%; right: 5%; }
.ib-f5 { bottom: 15%; left: 12%; }

.ib-hero-inner {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px;
}
.ib-hero-meta {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.ib-meta-badge {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
  background: var(--ib-neon); color: #000; padding: 6px 12px;
  letter-spacing: .2em;
}
.ib-meta-line { width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--ib-dim); }
.ib-meta-text {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .22em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: #666;
}

.ib-hero-title {
  font-family: var(--display); text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: clamp(80px, 14vw, 200px); line-height: .82;
  letter-spacing: -.02em; color: var(--ib-fg);
}
.ib-hero-title em {
  font-style: normal; color: var(--ib-neon);
  text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,255,136,.3);
}

.ib-hero-tagline {
  font-family: var(--body); font-size: 20px; margin-top: 30px;
  color: #999; font-weight: 300;
}
.ib-neon { color: var(--ib-neon); text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,136,.25); }

.ib-hero-desc {
  max-width: 560px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7;
  color: #777; margin-top: 20px;
}

.ib-hero-cta-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 40px; margin-top: 40px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.ib-cta-main {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  padding: 18px 32px; background: var(--ib-neon); color: #000;
  font-family: var(--mono); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: .2em; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none;
  transition: all .3s; cursor: pointer;
}
.ib-cta-main:hover {
  background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,255,136,.3);
}

.ib-hero-stats { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; }
.ib-hs { text-align: center; }
.ib-hs-n {
  display: block; font-family: var(--display); font-size: 24px;
  color: var(--ib-fg); line-height: 1;
}
.ib-hs-l {
  display: block; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: .2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #555; margin-top: 6px;
}
.ib-hs-div { width: 1px; height: 36px; background: var(--ib-dim); }

.ib-scroll-cue {
  position: absolute; bottom: 30px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  z-index: 2;
}
.ib-scroll-cue span {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .3em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: #444;
}
.ib-scroll-bar {
  width: 1px; height: 40px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--ib-neon), transparent);
  animation: ib-scroll-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes ib-scroll-pulse {
  0%,100% { opacity: .3; } 50% { opacity: 1; }
}

/* === MARQUEE === */
.ib-marquee {
  background: var(--ib-neon); overflow: hidden; padding: 14px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}
.ib-mq-track {
  display: flex; gap: 40px; white-space: nowrap;
  animation: ib-mq 30s linear infinite;
}
.ib-mq-w {
  font-family: var(--display); font-size: 28px; text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: .04em; color: #000;
}
.ib-mq-outline {
  -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px #000; color: transparent;
}
.ib-mq-dot { color: #000; font-size: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; }
@keyframes ib-mq { 0% { transform: translateX(0); } 100% { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

/* === STORY === */
.ib-story {
  background: var(--ib-bg); color: var(--ib-fg);
  padding: 120px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
}
.ib-story-grid {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: .8fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center;
}
.ib-story-lhs {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 30px;
}
.ib-lab-badge {
  position: relative; width: 180px; height: 180px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}
.ib-dna { width: 100%; height: 100%; animation: ib-rotate 20s linear infinite; }
@keyframes ib-rotate { 0% { transform: rotate(0); } 100% { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
.ib-lab-text {
  position: absolute; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .3em; text-align: center;
  color: var(--ib-neon); line-height: 1.2;
}
.ib-concept-tags {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; justify-content: center;
}
.ib-concept-tags span {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .15em;
  text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,136,.2); color: rgba(0,255,136,.5);
}

.ib-eyebrow {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .22em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ib-neon); margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.ib-eye-pulse {
  width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--ib-neon); animation: ib-pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes ib-pulse { 0%,100% { opacity:.4; } 50% { opacity:1; } }

.ib-story-h2 {
  font-family: var(--display); text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: clamp(44px, 5vw, 80px); line-height: .92;
}
.ib-story-h2 span { display: block; }
.ib-h2-neon { color: var(--ib-neon); text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,255,136,.2); }

.ib-story-p {
  color: #888; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 500px;
}

.ib-specs {
  margin-top: 36px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
}
.ib-spec {
  padding: 16px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;
}
.ib-spec:nth-child(odd) { border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06); }
.ib-spec-k {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .2em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: #555;
}
.ib-spec-v { font-family: var(--body); font-size: 14px; color: var(--ib-fg); font-weight: 500; }

/* === BENEFITS === */
.ib-benefits {
  background: var(--ib-bg); color: var(--ib-fg);
  padding: 100px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
}
.ib-benefits-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px;
}
.ib-benefits-h2 {
  font-family: var(--display); text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px); line-height: .92; margin-bottom: 48px;
}
.ib-benefits-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px;
}
.ib-benefit-card {
  padding: 32px 24px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,136,.12);
  background: rgba(0,255,136,.03); transition: border-color .3s;
}
.ib-benefit-card:hover { border-color: var(--ib-neon); }
.ib-benefit-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.ib-benefit-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--display); font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase;
